      public final void addAtBeginning​(java.lang.String annotatorClassName, UimaContextParameter... parameters)
      addAtBeginningg adds a pipeline annotator with its parameters to the pipeline. This is useful as a mechanism to re-use an already defined pipeline but add some pre-pipeline annotators to it.
      Parameters:
      annotatorClassName - the annotator class name
      parameters - variable number of parameter strings in key=value pairs to be passed to the annotator

    • addAtEnd

      public final void addAtEnd​(java.lang.String annotatorClassName, UimaContextParameter... parameters)
      addAtEnd adds a pipeline annotator with its parameters to the pipeline. This is useful as a mechanism to re-use an already defined pipeline but add some post-pipeline annotators to it. (This is a convenience method that is the same as the add method)
      Parameters:
      annotatorClassName - the annotator class name
      parameters - variable number of parameter strings in key=value pairs to be passed to the annotator

    • addAtEnd

      Parameters:
      pNumberOfInstances - the number of instances
      annotatorClassName - the annotator class name
      parameters - variable number of parameter strings in key=value pairs to be passed to the annotator
